.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, lily, azalea, daffodil
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, doctor, videographer, designer, journalist
There 5 different types of food: plum, mango, asparagus, raspberry, blueberry
City: miami, prague, boston, venice, berlin
1. the person who growszinnia is the person who likes red
2. the person who growsswedish is the person traveling to boston
3. the person who growsdahlia is the designer
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the doctor
6. the person eating asparagus is the person traveling to prague
7. the person who likes yellow is the person eating mango
8. the videographer is in the middle
9. the person who growsazalea is on the far left
10. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami
11. the person traveling to berlins is on the left or right of the person eating mango
12. the person eating plum is the accountant
13. the person who growslily is the person eating raspberry
14. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the journalist

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Flower	|   azalea	|    dahlia	|    zinnia	|    lily	|    swedish	|
| City		|     miami	|    berlin	|     prague	|     venice	|      boston	|
| Job	|    journalist	|     designer	|     videographer	|    doctor	|      accountant	|
| Food		|   mango	|    blueberry	|  asparagus	|    raspberry	|   plum	|
